  <brief_title>Primary vs. Secondary Anastomosis for Hinchey Stage III-IV Diverticulitis a Prospective Randomized Trial</brief_title>
  <acronym>DIVERTI</acronym>
  <official_title>Primary vs. Secondary Anastomosis After Sigmoid Colon Resection for Perforated Diverticulitis (Hinchey Stage III and IV): a Prospective Multicentric Randomized Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
